      • Group

        public Group(java.lang.String groupName,
             int groupDay,
             java.lang.String time)
      throws java.lang.Exception
        Class constructor initialising all values in class by copying.
        Parameters:
        groupName - initialises name, after checking if value doesn't containt forbidden hacking characters like ' or " by method Model.isHacker(String).
        groupDay - initialises day, after checking if value is corresponding class constraints.
        time - initialises start_hour and finish_hour by public method setTime(String), which checks if data is correct.
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception - in case of incorrect or hacking data this exception is thrown
